div.summary:
Article gives the results of the local elections: Burgess--I. H. McCauley;
                    Town Council--Charles Hutz, Calvin M. Duncan, Andrew Banker, Matthew Gillan,
                    James King; School Directors--Joseph Clark, D. K. Wunderlich, P. B. Houssum;
                    Borough Auditor--Wm. Adams; High Constable--George Gross. Article goes on to
                    discuss local political issues, such as town debt and city improvements, in a
                    sarcastic light.
